<h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
<p><strong>Effective date:</strong> July 21, 2026</p>
<p class="notice">These terms are a general business template and may need review by a qualified legal professional for your specific operations and local requirements.</p>

<h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
<p>By using the ATE ANNAS LAUNDRY website, online booking page or point-of-sale services, you agree to these Terms & Conditions.</p>

<h2>2. Laundry Services</h2>
<p>Services, prices, minimum weights, turnaround times, pickup schedules and delivery availability may change. Final charges are based on actual weighing, item count, service type and inspection.</p>

<h2>3. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
<p>Customers must provide accurate contact, address, schedule and garment information. Customers should remove valuables, cash, documents and fragile items from laundry before collection.</p>

<h2>4. Delicate, Damaged or Special-Care Items</h2>
<p>Customers must identify delicate, damaged, stained, color-sensitive or special-care items. ATE ANNAS LAUNDRY may decline items that are unsafe, contaminated or unsuitable for normal processing.</p>

<h2>5. Pickup and Delivery</h2>
<p>Pickup and delivery times are estimates and may be affected by traffic, weather, service volume or customer availability. Additional fees may apply based on location, distance or failed delivery attempts.</p>

<h2>6. Payments</h2>
<p>Accepted methods may include Cash, GCash, Maya and Bank Transfer. Digital payments may require a valid reference number. Orders may be held until full payment is confirmed.</p>

<h2>7. Claims and Order Release</h2>
<p>Customers should present the order code, claim stub or verified contact details before release. Any concern should be reported promptly after receiving the laundry.</p>

<h2>8. Unclaimed Orders</h2>
<p>Unclaimed orders may be subject to storage charges or other handling rules after reasonable notice, consistent with applicable law and posted store policy.</p>

<h2>9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
<p>ATE ANNAS LAUNDRY will exercise reasonable care. Liability, when legally applicable, may be limited to the fair value of the affected item or the service amount, subject to applicable law.</p>

<h2>10. Online Booking</h2>
<p>An online booking is a service request and is not final until confirmed. ATE ANNAS LAUNDRY may contact the customer to verify availability, address, schedule and service details.</p>

<h2>11. System Availability</h2>
<p>The website and POS may occasionally be unavailable due to internet interruption, maintenance or third-party service issues. Offline POS data may be stored locally on the device.</p>

<h2>12. Changes</h2>
<p>These terms may be updated. Continued use after changes means acceptance of the revised terms.</p>

<h2>13. Contact</h2>
<p>For questions, contact ATE ANNAS LAUNDRY through the contact details displayed on the website or receipt.</p>

